title: Cannot sync a .java file and another resource
description: When attempting to synchronize a .java file and another resource, the synchronization process fails.
OB: The synchronization of a .java file and another resource fails.
SR:
1. Open the synchronization tool.
2. Select a .java file and another resource to sync.
3. Initiate the synchronization process.
4. Observe the failure of the synchronization process.
